PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1774461962
OL,3,CArmed robber who was fought off by
OL,4,Cshopkeeper jailed
OL,6,FHe was identified from the CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage and pleaded guilty to robbery,
OL,8,Fpossessing an offensive weapon in a
OL,9,Fpublic place and possessing an
OL,10,Fimitation firearm.
OL,12,FA court heard he caused #380 of damage
OL,13,Fto the shop.
OL,15,FCarter-Ashton, of Lodge Road,
OL,16,FCarcroft, was jailed for six years and
OL,17,Feight months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
